~ start
if FillBarrel.has_barrel_to_fill()
	That jar is hard to reach!
	May I fill it for you?
	- Yes => help_accepted
	- No => help_denied
else
	You did it! => END

~ help_accepted
do FillBarrel.fill_barrel()
Bye!
do GameState.global.clear_help()
=> END

~ help_denied
OK, bye!
=> END
